# ## Common commit types
# - fix:      SemVer PATCH
# - feat:     SemVer MINOR
# - build:    Changes that affect the build system or external dependencies
# - ci:       Changes to CI related files and scripts
# - docs:     Documentation only changes
# - perf:     Code changes to improve performance
# - refactor: code changes that neither fix bugs nor add functionality
# - test:     Add missing tests or modify existing tests
#
# ## BREAKING CHANGES
# - SemVer MAJOR
# - can be part of commits of any type

# ## Resources
# - https://www.conventionalcommits.org
# - https://github.com/angular/angular/blob/22b96b9/CONTRIBUTING.md#-commit-message-guidelines
# - https://github.com/conventional-changelog/commitlint/tree/master/%40commitlint/config-conventional
